Conjuring trick-tier, but still neat:
The Alphanomics (or first step digital reduction) of any three digit repeating number, from 000 ... 999, multiplied by 37 produces that same number. 
Expressed inversely, dividing any such triple repeat number by 37 gives its AQ value.
